6056: /* Attempt to find the PSK (not session ticket) that matches.
6057:  *
6058:  * @param [in, out] ssl    The SSL/TLS object.
6059:  * @param [in]      psk    A pre-shared key from the extension.
6060:  * @param [out]     suite  Cipher suite to use with PSK.
6061:  * @param [out]     err    Error code.
6062:  *                         PSK_KEY_ERROR when key is too big or ticket age is
6063:  *                         invalid,
6064:  *                         UNSUPPORTED_SUITE on invalid suite.
6065:  *                         Other error when attempting to derive early secret.
6066:  * @return  1 when a match found - but check error code.
6067:  * @return  0 when no match found.

6052: 
6053:     return ret;
